    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The severity of periodontal recessions for each examined patient during dental consultation
      was evaluated. Moreover, the description of the number of periodontal recessions in patients
      with good health during dental consultation, the associated risk factors and evaluation of
      the number of recessions which need surgical therapy were realized.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
